<div class="inner" id="msg_1105931"><span style="font-size: 14pt;" class="bbc_size"><span style="color: brown;" class="bbc_color"><strong>海草海妖（Seaweed Siren），CR 13</strong></span></span><br><em>这种生物有三个不断唱歌的头在蛇形的脖子上摆动，蛇形的脖子从球茎状的身体延伸出来，身体中央被一张宽且有牙齿的嘴分开。</em><br><strong>出自</strong> Bestiary 4 pg. 235<br><strong><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color">XP&nbsp; 25600</span></strong><br>混乱中立 大型 魔法兽（水栖）<br><strong><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color">先攻</span></strong> +2; <strong><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color">感官</span></strong> 黑暗视觉60尺，昏暗视觉；察觉 +17<br><strong><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color">灵光</span></strong> 噪音（100尺，DC 22）<br><hr /><strong><span style="color: green;" class="bbc_color"><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size">防御</span></span></strong><br><strong><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color">AC</span></strong> 26，<span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>接触</strong></span> 11，<span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>措手不及</strong></span> 24 （+2 敏捷，+15 天生，-1体型）<br><strong><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color">hp</span></strong> 184（16d10+96）<br><strong><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color">强韧</span></strong> +16，<strong><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color">反射</span></strong> +12，<strong><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color">意志</span></strong> +8<br><strong><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color">免疫</span></strong> 影响心灵；<strong><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color">抗力</span></strong> 火焰 10，音波 10；<hr /><strong><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><span style="color: green;" class="bbc_color">攻击</span></span></strong><br><strong><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color">速度</span></strong> 30 尺，游泳 30 尺 <br><strong><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color">近战</span></strong> 啮咬 +25 (4d6+15/19-20)<br><strong><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color">远战</span></strong> 3 音波射线 +17 (4d6 音波)<br><strong><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color">特殊攻击</span></strong> 恍惚凝视，践踏(1d10+15, DC 28)<br><strong><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color">类法术能力</span></strong>&nbsp; (CL 16; 专注 +19)<br>&nbsp; &nbsp; 随意使用-<em>粉碎音波</em>（DC 16）<br>&nbsp; &nbsp; 3/每日-<em>魅惑怪物</em>（DC 18），瞬发<em>困惑术</em>（DC 18）<br>&nbsp; &nbsp; 1/每日-<em>降咒</em>&nbsp; (DC 18,远程接触攻击, 30 ft.)<br><hr /><strong><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><span style="color: green;" class="bbc_color">属性</span></span></strong><br><strong><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color">力量</span></strong> 30，<strong><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color">敏捷</span></strong> 15，<strong><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color">体质</span></strong> 22，<strong><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color">智力</span></strong> 11，<strong><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color">感知</span></strong> 16，<strong><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color">魅力</span></strong> 19<br><strong><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color">BAB</span></strong> +16；<strong><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color">CMB</span></strong> +27；<strong><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color">CMD</span></strong> 39（47 vs. 绊摔）<br><strong><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color">专长</span></strong> 盲斗，重击专攻，致聋重击，精通重击（啮咬），近距射击，猛力攻击，瞬发类法术（<em>困惑术</em>），技能专攻（察觉）<br><strong><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color">技能</span></strong> 唬骗+12， 察觉+17， 隐匿+17（+21在水中），游泳+18；<strong><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color">种族调整</span></strong> 在水中时隐匿+4<br><strong><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color">语言</span></strong>邪灵语，<em>巧言术</em><br><strong><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color">SQ</span></strong>假头，水域依赖<br><strong><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size">生态</span></span></strong><br><strong><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color">环境</span></strong> 任何海岸线<br><strong><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color">组织</span></strong> 单独<br><strong><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color">宝物</span></strong> 标准<hr /><strong><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><span style="color: green;" class="bbc_color">特殊能力</span></span></strong><br><strong><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color">噪音（Cacophony ，Su）：</span></strong> 海草女妖发出的噪音能干扰施法；在海草海妖100尺内施法时，必须通过一个专注检定（DC=15+即将施放法术的环位）才能正常施放。任何在该范围内进行的涉及听觉的察觉检定和其它专注检定的DC都会提升5点。海草海妖可以以一个自由动作开启或终止该能力。该能力是一个音波效果。<br><strong><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color">假头（False Heads ，Ex)）：</span></strong> 海草海妖的假头可以被切断。要切断一颗假头，对手需要对该假头用挥砍武器做出一次破武检定。一颗假头被视作一个具有0硬度和等同于海草海妖HD数HP（一般为16 hp）的单独武器。要切断该假头，对手需要对假头造成足以使hp降低至0或以下的伤害。切断一颗假头也会对海草海妖造成等同于HD数的伤害。海草海妖不能使用被切断的头发起攻击。失去所有假头的海草海妖不能使用噪音能力或任何类法术能力。<br><strong><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color">音波射线（Sonic Beams ，Su）：</span></strong>海草海妖的每一颗假头都能发射出一发射程60尺的射线，造成4d6音波伤害。<br><strong><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color">恍惚凝视（Staggering Gaze，Su）：</span></strong>造成恍惚，持续1d6轮，30尺射程，意志DC 22免除。该能力是一个影响心灵效果。该能力DC基于魅力。<br><strong><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color">水域依赖（Water Dependency，Ex）：</span></strong>海草海妖脱离水域之后，每点体质能令其存活1小时（一般为22轮<span style="color: green;" class="bbc_color">【译注：此处疑似笔误，个人认为以小时计算更合适】</span>）。超出此时间后，海草女妖将会开始窒息。<br><br><span style="color: purple;" class="bbc_color">海草海妖是一种利用上附肢上的假人头来引诱猎物的捕食者。这些假人头会在嘴里叽叽喳喳地说些无意义的话和无意中听到的句子片段。如果与它们交谈，它们会用类似语言的话来回应。这种行为让海草海妖在水下爬行，只露出头部，假装是游动的类人生物，直到它准备发起攻击之时。</span><br><br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i>原文</i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;"><a href="https://www.aonprd.com/MonsterDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Seaweed%20Siren" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">https://www.aonprd.com/MonsterDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Seaweed%20Siren</a><br>Seaweed Siren<br>This creature’s three singing heads sway atop serpentine necks that extend from a bulbous body split by a wide, toothy mouth.<br>Seaweed Siren CR 13<br>Source Bestiary 4 pg. 235, Pathfinder #60: From Hell&#039;s Heart pg. 90<br>XP 25,600<br>CN Large magical beast (aquatic)<br>Init +2; Senses darkvision 60 ft., low-light vision; Perception +17<br>Aura cacophony (100 ft., DC 22)<br>Defense<br>AC 26, touch 11, flat-footed 24 (+2 Dex, +15 natural, –1 size)<br>hp 184 (16d10+96)<br>Fort +16, Ref +12, Will +8<br>Immune mind-affecting effects; Resist fire 10, sonic 10<br>Offense<br>Speed 30 ft., swim 30 ft.<br>Melee bite +25 (4d6+15/19–20)<br>Ranged 3 sonic beams +17 (5d6 sonic)<br>Space 10 ft., Reach 5 ft.<br>Special Attacks staggering gaze, trample (1d10+15, DC 28)<br>Spell-Like Abilities (CL 16th; concentration +19)<br>At will—shatter (DC 16)<br>3/day—charm monster (DC 18), quickened confusion (DC 18)<br>1/day—bestow curse (DC 18, ranged touch attack, 30 ft.)<br>Statistics<br>Str 30, Dex 15, Con 22, Int 11, Wis 16, Cha 19<br>Base Atk +16; CMB +27; CMD 39 (47 vs. trip)<br>Feats Blind-Fight, Critical Focus, Deafening Critical, Improved Critical (bite), Point-Blank Shot, Power Attack, Quicken Spell- Like Ability (confusion), Skill Focus (Perception)<br>Skills Bluff +12, Perception +17, Stealth +17 (+21 in water), Swim +18; Racial Modifiers +4 Stealth in water<br>Languages Aklo; tongues<br>SQ false heads, water dependency<br>Ecology<br>Environment any coastlines<br>Organization solitary<br>Treasure standard<br>Special Abilities<br>Cacophony (Su) A seaweed siren’s noises disrupt spellcasting; casting within 100 feet of a seaweed siren requires a concentration check (DC 15 + the level of the spell being cast). All other concentration checks and Perception checks involving hearing made inside the aura have their DCs increased by 5. A siren can begin or end this ability as a free action. This is a sonic effect.<br><br>False Heads (Ex) A seaweed siren’s false heads can be severed. To sever a head, an opponent must make a sunder attempt with a slashing weapon targeting the head. A head is considered a separate weapon with hardness 0 and hit points equal to the siren’s Hit Dice (typically 16 hp). To sever a head, an opponent must deal enough damage to reduce the head’s hit points to 0 or fewer. Severing a head deals an amount of damage to the siren’s body equal to the siren’s Hit Dice. A siren can’t attack with a severed head. A siren with no remaining heads can’t use its cacophony ability or its spell-like abilities.<br><br>Sonic Beams (Su) Each of the siren’s false heads can fire a beam at a range of 60 feet, dealing 4d6 points of sonic damage.<br><br>Staggering Gaze (Su) Staggered 1d6 rounds, 30 feet, Will DC 22 negates. This is a mind-affecting effect. The save DC is Charisma-based.<br><br>Water Dependency (Ex) A seaweed siren can survive out of the water for 1 hour per point of Constitution (typically 22 rounds). Beyond this limit, a seaweed siren begins to suffocate.<br>Description<br>A seaweed siren is a predator that uses false humanlike heads on its upper appendages in order to lure prey. The heads babble nonsense words and fragments of overheard sentences. If spoken to, they respond with words from a similar language. This behavior allows the seaweed siren to creep about under the water with only the heads showing, pretending to be swimming humanoids until it is ready to attack.</div></div></div><br><br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i>这么猎奇的图片不能就我一个人看见！</i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width